The paper also addresses privacy concerns, which suggests that it could belong to the cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) sub-category. Additionally, the paper uses image datasets, indicating that it could also belong to the cs.CV (Computer Vision) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of adversarial learning, which is a popular technique in the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-category. Finally, the paper mentions the use of cloud-based services, which could suggest that it belongs to the cs.MM (Multimedia) sub-category.
